Revision history for Perl extension Catalyst::Plugin::I18N.

0.08  Wed Aug 06 2008
        - update dependency on I18N::LangTags

0.07  Mon Jan 07 2008
        - allow overriding of options sent to Locale::Maketext::Simple (RT #32132)
        - include a draft manual from a while back
        - Makefile.PL updates

0.06  Tue Jul 17 2007
        - re-org distro
        - switch to Module::Install
        - added language_tag() method
        - pod fixes

0.05  Sun Jan 09 2006
        - added language() method (Daisuke Murase)

0.04  Wed Nov 30 2005
        - added alias loc to localize
        - added Decode to Locale::Maketext::Simple import args
        - improved detecting of user locale
        - updated dependencies

0.03  Mon Nov 28 14:42:00 2005
        - added tests
        - doc fix

0.02  Fri Apr 15 16:17:00 2005
        - added doc tests.

0.01  Fri Jan 28 22:00:00 2005
        - first release
